    "title": "Maisha Baada ya Kifo",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "maisha baada ya kifo",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Waandishi wa Agano la Kale wanaelezea mahali ambapo wafu wako kama chini ya uso wa dunia (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek26:20\">Ezekieli 26:20</a>). Wakati mwingine, dunia inawameza wakiwa hai (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:31-Num16:33\">Hesabu 16:31–33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:15\">Zaburi 55:15</a>). Lakini mara nyingi, &quot;kamba za mauti&quot; zinawashusha &quot;na kuwameza&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:4-Ps18:5\">Zaburi 18:4–5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:30\">Hesabu 16:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job24:19\">Ayubu 24:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:14\">Zaburi 49:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:14\">Isaya 5:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:11\">14:11</a>). Katika Agano la Kale, maisha baada ya kifo mara nyingi yanaonekana kama mahali pa huzuni na kukata tamaa pasipo kurudi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job7:9\">Ayubu 7:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:18\">Isaya 38:18</a>).</p><p>Katika kitabu cha Ayubu, picha kuu kuhusu mahali pa wafu ni pamoja na:</p><ul><li><p><em>Sheol</em>, inayoelezewa kama mahali pa giza na vumbi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job11:8\">Ayubu 11:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job14:13\">14:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job17:13\">17:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job17:16\">16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job24:19\">24:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job26:6\">26:6</a>);</p></li><li><p>shimo lililojaa uozo (Kiebrania <em>shakhat</em>; tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job9:31\">9:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job17:14\">17:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:18\">33:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:22\">22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:24\">24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:28\">28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:30\">30</a>); na</p></li><li><p>kaburi (Kiebrania <em>qeber</em>; tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job3:22\">3:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:26\">5:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job10:19\">10:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job17:1\">17:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job21:32\">21:32</a>).</p></li></ul><p>Agano la Kale wakati mwingine linaonyesha wazo la kuokolewa kutoka kaburini (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:6\">1 Samweli 2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:10-Ps16:11\">Zaburi 16:10–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps30:3\">30:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:15\">49:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps56:13\">56:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:24-Ps73:26\">73:24–26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:13\">86:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:7-Ps139:10\">139:7–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:19\">Isaya 26:19</a>). Ayubu ana matumaini kwamba <em>Sheol</em> inaweza kupunguza shida zake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job3:13-Job3:22\">Ayubu 3:13–22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job14:13-Job14:17\">14:13–17</a>). Ana matumaini kwamba mkombozi anaweza kumtetea baada ya kifo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:25-Job19:26\">19:25–26</a>). Hata hivyo, ni Agano Jipya pekee linaloahidi ukombozi kamili kutoka kwa kifo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:50-1Cor15:58\">1 Wakorintho 15:50–58</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:6\">1 Samweli 2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:11-1Sam28:15\">28:11–15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:20-1Kgs17:22\">1 Wafalme 17:20–22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:32-2Kgs4:35\">2 Wafalme 4:32–35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job3:13-Job3:22\">Ayubu 3:13–22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job7:9\">7:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job14:13-Job14:17\">14:13–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job17:13-Job17:16\">17:13–16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:25-Job19:27\">19:25–27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps6:5\">Zaburi 6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:10-Ps16:11\">16:10–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps17:15\">17:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:15\">49:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:13\">86:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps88:11\">88:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:8\">139:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps141:7\">141:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:12\">Mithali 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:11\">15:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:19\">Isaya 26:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:18\">38:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek26:20\">Ezekieli 26:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:31-Matt22:32\">Mathayo 22:31–32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:23\">Warumi 8:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:50-1Cor15:58\">1 Wakorintho 15:50–58</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:21\">Wafilipi 3:21</a></p>",
